    "body" : "<p>You can use <a href=\"http://junit.sourceforge.net/javadoc/org/hamcrest/core/IsNull.html#nullValue()\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>IsNull.nullValue()</code></a> method:</p>\n<pre><code>import static org.hamcrest.Matchers.is;\nimport static org.hamcrest.core.IsNull.nullValue;\n\n\nassertThat(attr.getValue(), is(nullValue()));\n</code></pre>\n"
