    "body" : "<p>Use the following (from Hamcrest):</p>\n\n<pre><code>assertThat(attr.getValue(), is(nullValue()));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In Kotlin <code>is</code> is reserved so use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>assertThat(attr.getValue(), `is`(nullValue()));\n</code></pre>\n"
