    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want to <code>hamcrest</code>, you can do </p>\n\n<pre><code>import static org.hamcrest.Matchers.nullValue;\n\nassertThat(attr.getValue(), is(nullValue()));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In <code>Junit</code> you can do </p>\n\n<pre><code>import static junit.framework.Assert.assertNull;\nassertNull(object);\n</code></pre>\n"
